flowchart TD
  ST([Start]) --> LG{Logged in?}
  LG -- "No" --> LG1[Login screen<br/>Enter ID, password, OTP]
  LG1 --> LG2{Login success?}
  LG2 -- "Yes" --> HM[Home]
  LG -- "Yes" --> HM

  HM --> SYM[Select symbol<br/>Holdings plus today position]
  SYM --> S0[Open Sell order form]
  S0 --> SPROD{Product type?}
  SPROD -- "Delivery" --> SD_HOLD{Has holdings?}
  SD_HOLD -- "Yes" --> SD_QTY{Is sell qty more than holdings qty?}
  SD_QTY -- "Yes (holdings + today)" --> SD_POA_MIX{POA true?}
  SD_POA_MIX -- "No" --> SD_M_CDSL{CDSL already done for holdings qty?}
  SD_M_CDSL -- "Yes" --> SD_M1[Place Delivery Sell for full sell qty<br/>Holdings part covered by CDSL]
  SD_M1 --> SD_MOB[Record Sell in Order Book]
  SD_MOB --> SD_MFILL{Order executed?}
  SD_MFILL -- "Yes" --> SD_M_OK[Completed in Order Book]
  SD_M_OK --> SD_M_POS[Update positions<br/>Holdings reduced and todays position squared off]
  SD_M_POS --> SD_M_END[End<br/>POA false mixed qty with existing CDSL<br/>User sold full quantity]
